{"tid":742252,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"https://www.hk主持鍾晴嫌工廠狗污糟-言論被斥教壞人-其後fb發文道歉","createTime":"2018-07-14T11:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T11:47:13.000Z","uid":21716,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8655b08e32ac7fe986c1b116617835e6ba934d","tid":742252,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:32:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/寵物/210158/tvb主持鍾晴嫌工廠狗污糟-言論被斥教壞人-其後fb發文道歉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9%2F210158%2Ftvb%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E9%8D%BE%E6%99%B4%E5%AB%8C%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E7%8B%97%E6%B1%A1%E7%B3%9F-%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%A2%AB%E6%96%A5%E6%95%99%E5%A3%9E%E4%BA%BA-%E5%85%B6%E5%BE%8Cfb%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89&d=m8gd3gurkP6YbohuRWLU1zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=fb48a16f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/寵物/210158/tvb主持鍾晴嫌工廠狗污糟-言論被斥教壞人-其後fb發文道歉</a><br />\n<br />\nTVB兒童節目主持鍾晴（Karlie），在節目上失言，直指「工廠區嘅狗特別毛茸茸同污糟」、「即係&hellip;好乞人憎嗰啲啦」，引起網民圍攻，指她「教壞細路」。雖然怕狗對於某些人來說可能是自然反應，但如果公然對狗狗口出惡言，就可能會惹起公憤。<br />\n更新：鍾晴其後於7月13日下午，在Facebook發文道歉，表示當日的言論非常不成熟及欠缺社會責任 ，日後會慎言慎行。<br />\n7月11日播出的《兄弟幫》，TVB兒童節目《Think Big 天地》主持之一，鍾晴（Karlie）在訪談中分享節目拍攝點滴時，指自己除了龜以外，非常害怕其他動物。談及一次出外景時遇到大狗，鍾晴直言「你知，工廠區嘅狗特別毛茸茸同污糟」、「即係&hellip;好乞人憎嗰啲啦吓」。<br />\n她之後亦繼續分享其他遇狗經歷，曾試過遇上熱情狗狗，但仍感到不知所措，「朋友叫我扮唔好驚」、「因為狗見你驚就嚇你」、「都唔知佢咩心態」，主持人林盛斌（Bob）和陳國峰亦有打圓場，勸說「可能佢係善意呢」，連另一受訪者，同為《Think Big 天地》主持的鍾君揚亦出言「可能佢玩啫」，但鍾晴仍重申自己「真係好驚」。<br />\n片段在網上流傳後，惹起大量網民不滿，指鍾晴身為兒童節目主持人，卻不懂愛護和尊重動物，直斥她無資格做兒童節目主持，甚至會「教壞細路」，更有網民提供表格，希望集體向通訊事務管理局投訴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/193210_7cac4eec4a7f0bc0c4bc3ea225f4b435.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F193210_7cac4eec4a7f0bc0c4bc3ea225f4b435.png&h=a517b9ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/193211_6b3359220e3d30efc72d963cb7211667.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F193211_6b3359220e3d30efc72d963cb7211667.png&h=2cd2468e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/193213_824fa9c9b852fe83f636c14649cee544.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F193213_824fa9c9b852fe83f636c14649cee544.png&h=90505c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/193215_4c7efd674d5280f0aace91c74498ed1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F193215_4c7efd674d5280f0aace91c74498ed1d.png&h=f804666d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6aeb6118c74605156d09323fd70ecfa40ded187","tid":742252,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"佢呢隻公廁臭雞都好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b076c7b14f232ff4cb85c5e6c5a8ddd474d5399b","tid":742252,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"錯在唔虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0ff42dbacffee281dfb7fa95e31a376058cf60","tid":742252,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"宜家好多港女係咁啦"},{"pid":"28c6bae9a890b2e978443f8e3525b435fa21c58c","tid":742252,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"入得娛樂圈無得唔做偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b20ad8bcbf9b6e365907f8f291b86e6e657558e","tid":742252,"uid":139114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"希望佢知錯 下次改為講好憎老鼠/ 蜥蜴/昆蟲甚至雀仔 話佢哋好污糟核突 就唔會有人鬧佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貓狗係神聖不可侵犯㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30376b1f0e3c3279f598705b234328c9451fc1cf","tid":742252,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:41:01.000Z","msg":"on99 講事實有咩問題"},{"pid":"a08c504e2b004dcd24294e5499e7bc2c9c337ded","tid":742252,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:42:58.000Z","msg":"咁係吖嘛⋯⋯"},{"pid":"e460bb49b9c7cf43bc18d95b531664c6a9036ea7","tid":742252,"uid":102179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意都要話鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308195a118f121206044306a1b03ef2695746958","tid":742252,"uid":1349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T11:47:13.000Z","msg":"狗撚真係弱智"}]}